#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:1
msgid "Billing"
msgstr "Facturation"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:4
msgid ""
"Billing periods, INAMI packages, supplements, absences and invoices in "
"Resthome."
msgstr ""
"Périodes de facturation, forfaits INAMI, suppléments, absences et factures "
"dans Resthome."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:7
msgid ""
"Resthome automates MR/MRS billing: the **insurer's share** (INAMI package) "
"and the **resident's share** (accommodation + supplements), period by "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Resthome automatise la facturation MR/MRS : la **part mutuelle** (forfait "
"INAMI) et la **part résident** (hébergement + suppléments), période par "
"période."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:10
msgid "Key principles"
msgstr "Les grands principes"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:12
msgid ""
"**Billing period**: one month. You **generate** it, then **invoice** it."
msgstr ""
"**Période de facturation** : un mois. On la **génère**, puis on **facture**."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:13
msgid ""
"**INAMI package**: calculated from the **Katz category** and days of "
"presence; this is the share reimbursed by the insurer."
msgstr ""
"**Forfait INAMI** : calculé selon la **catégorie Katz** et les jours de "
"présence ; c'est la part remboursée par la mutuelle."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:15
msgid ""
"**Accommodation**: the share paid by the resident (the room), based on the "
"rate."
msgstr ""
"**Hébergement** : la part payée par le résident (la chambre), selon le "
"tarif."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:16
msgid ""
"**Supplements**: one-off or recurring services (single room, TV, "
"hairdresser…), through the resident's **supplements envelope**."
msgstr ""
"**Suppléments** : prestations ponctuelles ou récurrentes (chambre "
"individuelle, TV, coiffeur…), via l'**enveloppe de suppléments** du "
"résident."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:18
msgid ""
"**Absences**: an absence (hospitalisation, holidays) **reduces the package**"
" for the period concerned and can trigger an eHealth notification."
msgstr ""
"**Absences** : une absence (hospitalisation, vacances) **réduit le forfait**"
" sur la période concernée et peut déclencher une notification eHealth."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:21
msgid "Anticipatory billing"
msgstr "Facturation anticipative"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:24
msgid ""
"For residents billed in advance, one month's accommodation is invoiced **the"
" previous month**. The package and supplements, however, are invoiced in the"
" month of service."
msgstr ""
"Pour les résidents facturés en avance, l'hébergement d'un mois est facturé "
"**le mois précédent**. Le forfait et les suppléments, eux, sont facturés sur"
" le mois de prestation."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:29
msgid "The \"Refresh\" button"
msgstr "Le bouton « Actualiser »"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:31
msgid ""
"On a billing period, the **Refresh** action recalculates everything in one "
"click: billing lines, supplements and draft invoices."
msgstr ""
"Sur une période de facturation, l'action **Actualiser** recalcule tout en un"
" clic : lignes de facturation, suppléments et factures brouillon."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:34
msgid "Good to know"
msgstr "Bon à savoir"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:37
msgid ""
"Residents whose invoice is **already posted** are left untouched; everything"
" else is recalculated."
msgstr ""
"Les résidents dont la facture est **déjà comptabilisée** sont laissés "
"intacts ; tout le reste est recalculé."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:39
msgid ""
"Adding a supplement or an absence **synchronises automatically**: you "
"generally don't need to click \"Refresh\"."
msgstr ""
"Ajouter un supplément ou une absence se **synchronise automatiquement** : il"
" n'est en général pas nécessaire de cliquer « Actualiser »."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:43
msgid "The period cycle"
msgstr "Cycle d'une période"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:45
msgid "**New period** (the month)."
msgstr "**Nouvelle période** (le mois)."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:46
msgid "**Generate** the billing lines."
msgstr "**Générer** les lignes de facturation."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:47
msgid "Check the residents' **insurability (MDA)**."
msgstr "Vérifier l'**assurabilité (MDA)** des résidents."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:48
msgid "**Create the invoices** (resident's share)."
msgstr "**Créer les factures** (part résident)."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:49
msgid "**Post** the invoices."
msgstr "**Comptabiliser** les factures."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:50
msgid "**Generate the eFact** (insurer's share) then send it."
msgstr "**Générer l'eFact** (part mutuelle) puis l'envoyer."

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:52
msgid "Step by step"
msgstr "Pas à pas"

#: ../../content/facturation/index.md:55
msgid ""
"Follow the detailed guide [Invoicing a month, step by step](facturer-un-"
"mois.md), or see the whole [billing journey](../parcours-facturation.md)."
msgstr ""
"Suivez le guide détaillé [Facturer un mois, pas à pas](facturer-un-mois.md),"
" ou visualisez l'ensemble du [parcours de facturation](../parcours-"
"facturation.md)."

